snippet.title: Dungeon Zer0 - gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay of an old build of Dungeon Zer0 made by IER Studios in two weeks for a class project of Florida Universitaria.

Play the game for free on Windows PC and unite to the other 50 persons who have already enter the Dungeon for steal the legendary Magatama
https://ier-studios.itch.io/dungeon-zer0
